.SH NAME
std::experimental::erase_if(std::forward_list) \- std::experimental::erase_if(std::forward_list)

.SH Synopsis
   Defined in header <experimental/forward_list>
   template< class T, class Alloc, class Pred >              (library fundamentals TS
   void erase_if(std::forward_list<T,Alloc>& c, Pred pred);  v2)

   Erases all elements that satisfy the predicate pred from the container. Equivalent
   to c.remove_if(pred);

.SH Parameters

   c    - container from which to erase
   pred - predicate that determines which elements should be erased

.SH Complexity

   Linear.

